snippet.textDisplay:
Being An Awadhi Upian 🇮🇳, i feel this song is telling to find the pearl in your own self. But you are searching for it everywhere ,still dont dare to find that pearl in your own self.
I feel this bcoz even in Awadhi folk songs, we denote life as boat , consciousness as kevaiya(sailer) & pearl to our own true essence or truth😅.

This is also same with Bhojpuri folk songs (not movie)😊

Love our gujjus ❤
